text: Ronali Amatya (born 1996) in Kathmandu Nepal is a Nepali model and beauty pageant titleholder who won the title of Miss Nepal Interational 2018. She is 26th Miss Nepal International of the Nation. She has also won the Model Hunt Nepal in 2016 and won Miss Congeniality in Miss Rco International 2017 in Egypt. ==References== Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Nepalese models Category:Nepalese beauty pageant winners
